dc_title_s: C-08 Geologic atlas of Fillmore County, Minnesota [Parts A and C]
dc_description_s: 5 pls. Scale 1:100,000. Pl. 1, data-base; pl. 2, bedrock geology; pl. 3, surficial geology; pl. 4, depth to bedrock and bedrock topography; pl. 5, geologic resources. Part B Published separately by the Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters. Part C is the text supplement for C-8. Supplementary files include ESRI GIS coverages pertaining to the geology plates.
